entry.title: Special Weather Statement issued November 10 at 3:46AM AKST by NWS
entry.summary: ...FREEZE UP ICE JAMS ONGOING IN ANCHORAGE BOWL AND MAT-SU VALLEY... Recent abnormally cold temperatures have caused many rivers and streams across the Anchorage and Mat-Su areas to rapidly freeze up. This has caused ice jams to form on some waterways leading to localized overflow flooding in vicinity of the ice jams.
